snippet.title: RalliSport Challenge 2 60FPS Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution VIII Rally Sweden (Snow) Clean
snippet.description:
RalliSport Challenge 2 60FPS 720p Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution VIII Rally Sweden (Snow) Clean

Track: Sweden / SS1 - Bockfors.
I tried to beat my best time of 01:53.959 for this video but I couldn't do it. I must have restarted over 300x. This is the cleanest, fastest run I could get at 01:54.518  

Played on the original Xbox with an original Xbox controller. Gameplay captured using an Elgato Capture HD. Recorded in 720x480p at 59fps. Upscaled to 1280x720p at 59fps to get 60fps (with chrome). Aspect ratio is 4:3 centered, not cropped. It's not HD but at 60fps this is as close to the original quality that you can get!
